inoremap <C-A> <ESC>ggVG
vnoremap <C-A> <ESC>ggVG 

" Shift+arrow selection
nmap <S-Up> v<Up>
nmap <S-Down> v<Down>
nmap <S-Left> v<Left>
nmap <S-Right> v<Right>
vmap <S-Up> <Up>
