imap <S-Right> <Esc><Right>v

" Ctrl+backspace to delete prev word, ctrl+del to delete next word
inoremap <C-H> <C-\><C-o>db
inoremap <C-Del> <C-\><C-o>dw

" Indentation
vmap <lt> <gv
vmap > >gv

" Turn off search highlight until next search
nnoremap <F3> :noh<CR>

" Repeat prev macro
nmap , @@

